title: Mikolo LAT Pulldown Machine, LAT Machine Home Gym with Scissor Style, 800lbs Upper Body Strength Trainer with Adjustable Seat and Leg Axles, Commercial-Grade Back Machine with Multi-Grip Handles
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Upper Body Machines
features: [Sculpt Your Upper Body] Ditch ordinary lat pull-downs for the innovative Scissor Lat pull-down! When users train on this scissor-style lat pulldown machine, they don't just pull the handles from high to low like they would with traditional lat pulldown machines. Instead, they can also pull them from wide to narrow – a feature that traditional lat pulldown machines simply don't have. Its entire movement path follows the direction of the back's muscle fibers more naturally

[Dynamic Scissor Motion] Experience a unique workout sensation with the scissor motion design, which offers a smooth and natural range of motion. This innovative movement pattern maximizes muscle activation, the more natural movement path reduces the rotational stress on the shoulder joints and pressure on the elbow joints during normal pulldown motions

[Isolateral Exercise] The independent arm design allows for isolated stimulation of the back muscles on each side, reducing the compensation that can occur in the final stages of exhaustion when using a straight bar or V-shaped handle, where the stronger side often compensates for the weaker side, thereby minimizing the occurrence of uneven muscle tension across the back

[Dual Grip Design] This Back machine has both wide and narrow grips. Users can choose based on their needs. The wide grip emphasizes outer/upper lats, engages posterior deltoids & biceps, suitable for those with good shoulder flexibility wanting to widen back. The narrow grip targets lower/mid-lats more, reduces shoulder joint outward pressure, ideal for those with shoulder discomfort or aiming to ease shoulder strain

[Adjustable Design] The lat machine features a 5-position adjustable leg holder and a 11-position adjustable seat, making it more accommodating for users with different arm spans and leg lengths. The weight-loading system is also suitable for users of various training levels, especially beginners who may struggle with bodyweight pull-ups and have less strength

[Cross-base design] Mikolo lat pulldown machine features a cross-base design with a measurement of 52.88” Depth x 42.11” Width x 77.84” Height and a total footprint of 15.46 square feet, this size is similar to a storage cabinet. Compared to typical structures, this design reduces the footprint while providing greater stability, allowing the machine's weight to be evenly distributed across the base, thereby preventing machine wobbling during use

description: The Plated-Loaded Lat Tower is a space-saving strength trainer designed to build your back and shoulder strength. This high-quality Lat Tower combines lat pull down and a low row position, making it a smart addition to any home gym. With dual, 13-inch loadable weight plate sleeves, you can slowly work up to higher intensity workouts with a weight capacity of up to 400-pounds. title: Body Solid (LVLA) Leverage LAT Pulldown Machine Includes Weight Plate Holders, Commercial and Home Gym Machines and Workout Equipment for Upper Body Exercises
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness
description: The Body-Solid Leverage Lat Pulldown Machine (LVLA) features a dual-axis diverging arm for biomechanically correct lat pulldowns that target your back, arm, and shoulder muscles. 360-degree articulating hand grips float freely and rotate naturally while you pull. Adjustable leg hold-down pads and gas-assisted seat adjustments allow the machine to be operated by users of all sizes.With a 2- by 3-inch 11-gauge high-tensile strength steel mainframe and durable double-stitched upholstery, this lat exercise machine is durably constructed to stand up to rigorous use in gyms and clubs. Sealed bearing pivot points provide smooth, friction-free movement through every intense workout. Weight plate holders are built into the machine for easy storage (plates sold separately).When assembled, the Body-Solid Leverage Lat Pulldown Machine measures 76 by 49 by 84 inches (L x W x H) and weighs 183 pounds. It is backed by the Body-Solid Lifetime In-Home Warranty and Full Commercial Warranty.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bike machine, ellipticals, cage workout rack, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

EFFORTLESS STRENGTH BUILDING: Transform your workouts with Body Solid's unique dual-axis diverging arm movement, allowing for a full range of motion that targets every muscle effectively with this lat pull-down machine home gym. Ideal for enhancing upper body strength, this pulldown machine is perfect for targeting the latissimus dorsi, biceps, and upper back.

HAND GRIPS FOR VARIOUS POSITIONS: The 360-degree articulating hand grips on the Body Solid lat machine ensure an ergonomically superior experience by adapting to your natural hand positions. This setup also reduces strain and improves comfort during each rep while focusing on specific muscle groups.

UNMATCHED VERSATILITY FOR FULL-BODY WORKOUTS: Whether you're focusing on lats, biceps, shoulders, or more, this machine allows for an extensive range of exercises, making it an indispensable part of any home gym equipment collection. Enjoy the freedom to switch up your routines and target multiple muscle groups effectively, ensuring well-rounded fitness development.

DURABILITY THAT LASTS: Experience the robust construction of this Body Solid lat pull down machine designed to withstand intense workouts and long-term use. Built with high-quality materials, it's crafted to provide stability and robustness, offering peace of mind with every pull. The integrated weight plate holders provide a convenient solution for weight storage, while making it a lot easier to switch weights in between exercise routines. Dimensions: 84" L x 54" W x 81" H

description: Mikolo Folding Squat Rack, Wall Mounted Power Rack with Cable Crossover Machine & LAT Pull Down, Power Cage with 5 Adjustable Function Modes, Upgraded Home Gym Package
features: [SPACE-EFFICIENT MARVEL]: Maximize your space with our folding squat rack! Expandable to a mere 9.5 SQ.FT when fully opened, and folding down to just 3 SQ.FT when not in use, it's the ultimate solution for home gyms, cramped basements, or cozy family garages. Perfect for those who crave quality workouts in tight quarters, it's your compact yet powerful fitness ally!

[ALL-IN-ONE MACHINE]: This ingenious machine seamlessly integrates a power rack, cable crossover machine, lat pulldown machines, pull-up bar, and more into one sleek unit. With five adjustable settings - folded, semi-open, power rack, functional trainer, and cable crossover machine - you have the versatility to tackle any workout.

[DUAL CABLE CROSSOVER]: This independent pulley system lets you effortlessly perform super sets and drop sets without being limited by your home gym's weight stack. You can also train with friends or family, sharing the sweat and excitement. With a 1:1 pulley ratio, the cable machine saves you the expense of additional high-resistance equipment and takes the guesswork out of calculating your actual training load.

[UNRIVALED STABILITY]: Crafted from 2x2 inch 14-gauge steel, with reinforced screw-in wall mounts and four adjustable ground support feet, this wall mounted squat rack is built to handle up to 1000lbs with ease, ensuring your safety during the most intense workouts, which minimizes the risk of instability that often plagues traditional power racks under heavy loads. Plus, with a premium pulley system, you can enjoy smooth, seamless movement every time.

[FULL BODY WORKOUTS]: Complete with a detachable pull-up bar, premium J hooks, and a single-handed adjustable pulley system offering 15 height options, this squat rack home gym is designed for versatility and convenience. With over 80 different full-body exercises including squats, bench presses, seated rows, cable flies, bicep curls, kickbacks, and more, it's the perfect choice for fitness enthusiasts seeking a comprehensive workout experience.

What is the minimum ceiling height I need? 
Machine height is 87.2'', the minimum ceiling height to be able to do a full pull up with your head above the pull-up bar is 102''. 
Does the M4 take up a lot of space? 
No, it just takes up only 23.64 square feet of space. 
What is the pulley ratio? 
The pulley ratio is 2:1, meaning if you have 100 pounds loaded, the resistance is 50 pounds. M4 is equipped with dual independent cable systems. Loading capacity of cable system: 400 Pounds on each side. 
How to bench press heavy without a spotter? 
M4 comes with 6mm thick safety catches and safety stoppers, and 10 height adjustments. Set the safety stoppers just above chest height as the barbell is lowered. If you fail, the stopper will catch the bar, preventing it from crushing you.

Product Description
GYHPD LAT Power Cable Machine 
The High and Low Pulley Station is quick and easy to assemble, has a small footprint, is perfect for home gyms, combines Lat pull-downs and low rowing positions, and is designed to build back and upper body strength, with a maximum weight capacity of 440 lbs. 
LAT Pull Down 
The LAT pull down handle can be used in a standing or seated position to work your upper body and back muscles, and is designed with two hooks on the top of the machine to help make it easy to hang it back up. 
Row Handle 
The row handle can also be used in a standing or seated position for seated bicep curls and seated rows, and is designed with hooks under the seat for easy storage. 
Low Row Pedal 
Designed for low row training, this pedal has a diamond shaped texture that increases friction underfoot and won't slip, so you can enjoy your training with peace of mind. 
Adjustable Seat and Leg Cushions 
Seat cushion with three adjustable heights from 17“-21”. Leg cushions are four-position adjustable from 24.8“-26.8”. 
Adjustable Moving Pulley 
Designed with four adjustment holes, you can change the length of the cable by changing the up and down position of the pulley. Smooth pulley system for a great pulling experience. 
With Sleeve 
The weight bar is 1“ in diameter with a 2” sleeve and weight storage pins to accommodate standard and Olympic plates up to 200 lbs. per side.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
The Synergee Lat Pulldown Pulley Machine with Seat is a one-stop-shop for gains. With a 250 lb weight capacity, 3 different exercise zones, adaptable loading pins, and multiple handles, you will not regret adding this machine to your home gym set up. 
The Synergee Lat Pulldown Machine is a free-standing cable machine. It has 3 distinct zones for different workouts. The Top Exercise Zone provides a Lat Bar for pull-downs. Plus, a removable seat can be installed and quad rollers can be put to use if you want to perform them seated. The Mid Exercise Zone is the spot to perform weighted crunches, made extra comfortable by the padded harness with handles that’s included with the machine. The Lower Exercise Zone provides everything you need for standing rows, seated rows, curls and kick back. The handles provided with this machine are interchangeable, so you can set them at the height you need for your unique workout routines. Plus, the universal attachment points means any other cable workout handles can also be used on machine. 
This machine is 58.3” (L) x 24.2” (W) x 77.0” (H). It comes with loading pins and adaptors to hold 1”- and 2”-opening weight plates. The pulley system is made with premium nylon cables and the structure is constructed with 11 gauge steel to provide a strong, sturdy workout station. This commercial gym-level piece of equipment will allow you to reach new levels of fitness from your own home. 
STRONG & STURDY 
This Pulley Machine is made with premium nylon cables and 11 gauge steel to provide a 250 lb weight capacity and a machine that won’t quit. Lift heavy and lift often knowing this machine can support every rep, and it’s got tons of capacity to accommodate your growing gains! 
TAKE A SEAT! 
This Pulley Machine provides a padded seat that you can use for crunches, pull downs, and more! It can easily be installed or removed; so it’s there when you need it, and gone when you need to utilize that space for other workouts. The seat is comfortable and integral for getting effective reps in. 
CRUNCH HARNESS 
This harness has got it all: handles for a comfortable grip, padding to protect those shoulders, universal attachment point to clip in or remove with ease. It will make you WANT to do core work! This harness makes crunches comfortable and allows you target your core with less strain than traditional crunches. 
TOP EXERCISE ZONE 
Get those lats, delts, and traps working in the Top Exercise Zone! The top portion of our Pulley Machine provides a Lat Bar for wide or narrow pull downs. Do them standing, or add the cushioned seat to perform them seated. 
MID EXERCISE ZONE 
Clip in the Crunch Harness and lock in that seat: it’s core crunching time! Add weight to the loading pins and activate your core by utilizing the Mid Exercise Zone on this Pulley Machine. A strong core is integral to strength gains overall! 
LOWER EXERCISE ZONE 
The Lower Exercise Zone provides you with the widest range of exercises: it’s got a straight bar to perform standing rows and curls. Or, sit on the floor with your feet on the lower platform and knock out some seated rows. This Zone can also be a spot for leg workouts like kick backs and leg curls.
